title: Varand, Iran
text: Varand () is a village in <a href="Tangeh%20Soleyman%20Rural%20District">Tangeh Soleyman Rural District</a>, <a href="Kolijan%20Rostaq%20District">Kolijan Rostaq District</a>, <a href="Sari%20County">Sari County</a>, <a href="Mazandaran%20Province">Mazandaran Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 219, in 68 families.
